​̲𝑹​̲𝒆​̲𝒂​̲𝒍​̲-​̲𝑻​̲𝒊​̲𝒎​̲𝒆​̲ ​̲𝑳​̲𝒆​̲𝒂​̲𝒇​̲ ​̲𝑫​̲𝒊​̲𝒔​̲𝒆​̲𝒂​̲𝒔​̲𝒆​̲ ​̲𝑫​̲𝒆​̲𝒕​̲𝒆​̲𝒄​̲𝒕​̲𝒊​̲𝒐​̲𝒏​̲ ​̲𝒗​̲𝒊​̲𝒂​̲ ​̲𝑾​̲𝒆​̲𝒃​̲𝒄​̲𝒂​̲𝒎 | ​̲𝑶​̲𝒑​̲𝒆​̲𝒏​̲𝑪​̲𝑽​̲ ​̲+​̲ ​̲𝑫​̲𝑳

A computer vision module that uses webcam feed to detect plant diseases in real-time using a pretrained MobileNetV2 deep learning model.


✅ 𝑭𝒆𝒂𝒕𝒖𝒓𝒆𝒔:

- 📷 Real-time webcam stream (𝐎𝐩𝐞𝐧𝐂𝐕)
- 🔍 Frame-by-frame leaf disease detection
- 🧠 Pretrained CNN model (𝐌𝐨𝐛𝐢𝐥𝐞𝐍𝐞𝐭𝐕𝟐)

---

🔍 𝑴𝒐𝒅𝒆𝒍 & 𝑰𝒏𝒕𝒆𝒈𝒓𝒂𝒕𝒊𝒐𝒏:

- 🧠 Model: Pretrained MobileNetV2 fine-tuned for leaf disease detection using the PlantVillage dataset
- 📦 Dependencies: OpenCV, TensorFlow, Streamlit

---

💻 𝑻𝒆𝒄𝒉 𝑺𝒕𝒂𝒄𝒌:

| 𝐂𝐨𝐦𝐩𝐨𝐧𝐞𝐧𝐭    | 𝐓𝐨𝐨𝐥/𝐋𝐢𝐛𝐫𝐚𝐫𝐲       |
|---------------|-------------------|
| DL Inference  | TensorFlow        |
| Real-time Feed| OpenCV            |
| UI Dashboard  | Streamlit         |
| Model Source  | PlantVillage DL   |

---

🧪 𝑾𝒐𝒓𝒌𝒇𝒍𝒐𝒘 𝑺𝒖𝒎𝒎𝒂𝒓𝒚:

1. Launch webcam using OpenCV  
2. For each frame:
   - Preprocess → Resize, Normalize  
   - Predict using DL model  
   - Display output label in real-time  

